{"tid":2127334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部批評美方不斷炒作所謂「中國滲透」言論","createTime":"2020-07-27T09:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:24:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7b6f3d83636ce3d9f333fddabf046d6cab2e7c","tid":2127334,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"一名新加坡公民在美國法庭承認為中國做代理人收集情報，法庭將於十月裁決。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌表示，對事件不太了解，但美方執法部門為了抹黑打壓中國，近來不斷炒作所謂的「中國滲透」言論及中國間諜問題，已達致草木皆兵﹑杯弓蛇影的地步。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌又說，美方在全球範圍內大搞間諜殲滅活動，連自己的盟友也不放過，敦促美方停止賊喊捉賊，不要再污衊中國。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540128-20200727.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540128-20200727.htm&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=e141e309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540128-20200727.htm&h=fcfd3ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540128-20200727.htm</a>"},{"pid":"585be6d86ee4f559fcf37f2e7083f544f5b0a347","tid":2127334,"uid":79117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d7f1f8ee798d0d97931ca01a6a4aa9ec198ba0c","tid":2127334,"uid":8542,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"對事件不太了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a160471481b1c7b90d40c78037c3c5975758a0","tid":2127334,"uid":146285,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"講乜春野都加個''所謂''係前面.<br />\n呢個所謂既中國真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf418bc75821a55ce252579050220f15430d8b5","tid":2127334,